channel.title: [Request] Autofighter for low level
channel.description:
I need an autofighter for somewhere, low levels. I don't have any food to eat. I was wondering if there was a death walk-back option, auto-equip, etc. Somewhere like the Men in edgeville, Al kharid warriors, something.
I might be able to get some RS2 GP together if someone could help me out. Thanks. <3
Oh, I need the script to work for hours, thanks guys.

item.title: [Request] Autofighter for low level
item.dc:creator: @TheDarkMage TheDarkMage
item.description:
@TheDarkMage wrote:

get kuroro or fagex autofighter. The retail version of fagex autofighter can run for weeks without dying in it are functions like running away when your hp is low, logging out when it’s way too low, autoeating, autochatting, autologin, autologout, antirandoms, auto camera rotater, and even more! If you can’t buy the retail version you could get it illegally, but if you do i’m not responsible for any action you take! Check out www.rs2cheating.com and www.autofighter.org
